window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Nicola Marter was born with a gift. When she touches an object, she sometimes glimpses those who have owned it before. When a woman arrives with a small wooden carving at the gallery Nicola works at, she can see the objectâ€™s history and knows that it was named after the Firebird - the mythical creature from an old Russian fable. </p> <p>Compelled to know more, Nicola follows a young girl named Anna who leads her into the past on a quest through the glittering backdrops of the Jacobites and Russian courts, unearthing a tale of love, courage, and redemption.</p>"; 
